The quaternion formulation of the composition of two rotations RB and RA also yields directly the rotation axis and angle of the composite rotation RC = RBRA.

Let the quaternion associated with a spatial rotation R is constructed from its rotation axis S and the rotation angle &quot;φ&quot; this axis. The associated quaternion is given by,

:formula_157

