== Lie algebra structure ==
As noted above, the Lie algebra formula_5 of consists of skew-Hermitian matrices with trace zero.

The complexification of the Lie algebra formula_5 is formula_69, the space of all complex matrices with trace zero. A Cartan subalgebra then consists of the diagonal matrices with trace zero, which we identify with vectors in formula_70 whose entries sum to zero. The roots then consist of all the permutations of .

